{"tid":877461,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果收購新創公司 Spektral，主打即時「綠幕」技術","createTime":"2018-10-26T11:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T16:25:48.000Z","uid":109383,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"14d3705f44ccc458f80c629e62b421ff87fb8e02","tid":877461,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"根據 B&oslash;rsen 消息，蘋果已收購丹麥電腦視覺新創公司 Spektral。Spektral 開發了一種可將照片和影片中人和物體與初始背景智慧地分開、以新背景覆蓋，進而達成「剪下」的功能。此解決方案由深度神經網路和譜圖理論驅動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/190123_7cc882f3de4539d0a0c3256d6833e440.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F190123_7cc882f3de4539d0a0c3256d6833e440.png&h=cf24aab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此技術可視為由機器學習演算法驅動的即時「綠幕」處理，Spektral 開創性和獨特技術基於最先進的機器學習和電腦視覺技術。將深度神經網路和頻譜圖理論與現代 GPU 的計算能力結合，引擎可直接在裝置即時（60FPS）處理來自相機的影像和影片。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，蘋果於 2017 年底收購 Spektral，前身為 CloudCutout。Spektral 聯合創始人 Henrik Paltoft 和 Toke Jansen 現在的職位是蘋果電腦成像經理。消息稱，蘋果收購的價格為 3,000 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\nSpektral 官網提到，其解決方案可建立獨特且身臨其境的混合實境（MR）內容。蘋果可將此技術整合到 iPhone 預設相機、資訊或立可拍應用，還能將技術用於擴增實境項目。"},{"pid":"764bfb43ecc4ced95015994bb6916e6ae66e2630","tid":877461,"uid":200872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要買新機"},{"pid":"1a4282522e2636c2be8a29234e418018043c3673","tid":877461,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"係唔係講緊「退地」？"},{"pid":"8d13277b6122656ee43769b7dc644a5905a1c92e","tid":877461,"uid":9838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"係幾勁既"},{"pid":"d122a67ebc95c90426d1feb39f15d526631e7f1e","tid":877461,"uid":65371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"即時綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc91e84830a5a313480e2ebe5eb45658e48fb08d","tid":877461,"uid":9838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a4282522e2636c2be8a29234e418018043c3673","tid":877461,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"係唔係講緊「退地」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"類似<br />\n<br />\n即時綠幕係將背景換做其他野，主體不變"},{"pid":"28fe4e0a369c2c6bc720418897b1371f5e99ecfe","tid":877461,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁講相好易做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484eb6e25620b324d6f97e1429a9d7bd3d68ef72","tid":877461,"uid":73310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"28fe4e0a369c2c6bc720418897b1371f5e99ecfe","tid":877461,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁講相好易做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"明眼人一睇就知啊嬌比人屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e81618bff84362e7855e97b90b37aa8850dbed","tid":877461,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484eb6e25620b324d6f97e1429a9d7bd3d68ef72","tid":877461,"uid":73310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"28fe4e0a369c2c6bc720418897b1371f5e99ecfe","tid":877461,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁講相好易做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"明眼人一睇就知啊嬌比人屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"仆街killer搭時光機買iPhone屈阿嬌咁無恥?!!"},{"pid":"66e124657336af878c678933732c1f1bdfd4b812","tid":877461,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"偷食個陣更加易虛報行蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/